Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:10.90,1080P思源-7,,0,0,0,,英文字幕:\h官方\N翻译: 谷歌翻译\N润色，压制:\hBolshevik0
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:35.94,1080P思源-7,,0,0,0,,吐槽:\h不改变已有载具数据???喵喵喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:10.90,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Hi everybody. My name is Kirill Yudintsev. I'm the creative director at Gaijin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:16.38,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,and right now I'd like to tell you a little about the latest update 1.77, Advancing Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,0:00:23.70,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We've had a lot of feedback about the latest update. Thanks for writing to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:26.32,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Your feedback is very important and useful to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:33.94,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs35}Among other things, a lot of the feedback was about the new engine, the new renderer, the new graphics, and the changes to the game's performance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:37.80,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Performance has improved for some players and become worse for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:43.46,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}Some of the players who experienced worse performance were using supersampling (SSAA x4).
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:47.66,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Supersampling is the most resource-intensive form of anti-aliasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:54.40,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs47}We don't recommend enabling it unless your video card is very powerful and you get at least 200 FPS without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:01:01.06,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs43}For everyone else there are options that are simpler in terms of performance and can provide results that are just as good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:06.04,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,HQ TAA, just TAA, or even HQ FXAA.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:11.26,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,These are perfectly decent types of anti-aliasing that provide very nice image quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:23.26,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs51}The new engine has given the game a lot of new capabilities, but we've still got some things to work on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:25.84,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,and there's definitely room to improve optimization
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:31.64,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs51}these new capabilities require a lot of configuration and we need to take a lot of nuances into account.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:35.62,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,The update just came out, and at some point over the next six months
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:40.24,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs56}we're going to improve various aspects of the game's appearance, as well as its performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:46.18,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs50}So if your performance has gotten worse, it's possible that we'll be able to find a way to improve it in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:53.68,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs45}A large number of players have been asking about the navy, how the pre-cbt of the War Thunder navy has been going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:57.06,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,what its eventual fate will be, and what our future plans are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:02.86,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs50}Testing is going well. We've done a lot, and we don't have all that much left on our to-do list, in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.82,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,we're approaching getting in to closed beta testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:09.00,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,The naval has changed profoundly over the last two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:14.88,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs54}It has traveled a long road from what it was at the beginning of CBT and what it has become now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:20.12,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,And it's all happened exclusively thanks to our players, their feedback, and their opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:24.28,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs54}We've been listening to them, we've watched them play, and we've tested and played with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:36.38,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs49}Our goal is to make everything fun and engaging, and we don't want naval play to disappoint our players.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.88,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We want it to satisfy their expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:42.70,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,As far as we're concerned, we've achieved almost everything we could
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:45.44,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,everything we wanted, and everything our players wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:48.62,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,In other words, we're at the end of this initial stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.86,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Our players often ask what our future plans are for aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:03:01.04,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs43}They want to know why we keep coming out with all sorts of things, including modern vehicles, for tank commanders,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:03.52,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,but when it comes to aircraft there's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:09.04,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,The first thing I should point out is that before we introduced ground vehicles
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:13.26,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,we dedicated about four years exclusively to developing the aviation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:20.58,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Another four years have passed since we introduced ground vehicles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:24.60,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs59}and during that time we've never stopped developing both parts of the game in parallel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:30.78,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs41}It's just that the majority of the most important things we could have implemented for aircraft have already been implemented.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:34.54,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We've been adding some rather significant things every year, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.96,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,we introduced gunner cockpits relatively recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:44.44,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs47}and we made it possible for planes to be destroyed by midair collisions with falling bombs in the same update.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:55.24,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs38.9}In general, we've been introducing all sorts of things, but they're mostly smaller things because all the big stuff has already been done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:04:00.20,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}The next major step we can take when it comes to aircraft will probably be noticed by everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:07.28,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs38.9}I'm talking about switching to more modern supersonic planes and introducing guided missiles and other modern aviation technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:17.40,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,As I said earlier, we've been conducting and are continuing to conduct internal testing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.42,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,and the results aren't exactly unambiguous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:27.02,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs48}Vehicles on this level make things complicated thanks to missiles, detection systems, and supersonic speeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:42.12,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs38}All of our players who fly planes know that jet planes are already significantly different from piston-engine planes in terms of gameplay,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:45.14,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,and there are plenty of people who don't like this difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:49.86,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Future changes will alter the game even more, so we're working, we're testing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:55.12,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs54}and right now I'm not ready to say that more modern aircraft will definitely appear in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:59.92,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs59}But there's still a good chance that more modern planes of some kind will be introduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:05.32,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,I can't give you any details, we're still in the research and experimentation phase
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.52,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,with the goal of determining the "upper limit."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:12.46,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs56}There's also the issue that there are fewer and fewer different production models of vehicles,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:15.44,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,so balancing various nations becomes problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:21.62,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs52}There are a lot of nuances and questions, and this is an extremely complex task in terms of gameplay
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.64,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,balance, and how to explain it all to our players.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:35.94,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,As you know, we don't invent new vehicles or change the stats of existing ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:41.70,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs51}so if balance was an issue in real life, then it's also going to be a problem with the vehicles in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:47.58,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs51}In general, there's a lot of work, and most of our players won't necessarily be pleased with the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.88,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,That being said, in our game you don't need to play with every vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:55.06,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,if there's something you don't like, don't play with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:06:02.88,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs47}so we're still working on this for players who will like it, but I can't tell you more about certain plans right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:09.30,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs58}In addition, we're also experimenting with helicopters, both attack helicopters and others
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:13.28,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,and here things are looking much more positive and unambiguous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:18.98,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,This kind of gameplay will generally be simpler and more understandable for players.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:24.38,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}Although helicopters are harder to fly than planes, they're also slower and have less firepower
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:34.58,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs56}Shorter firing distances, and the pilot's influence in terms of piloting and shooting is greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:39.86,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs58}So it's entirely possible that helicopters will appear in our game before modern planes do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:45.56,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs46}They also fit better with ground vehicles in terms of destroying each other, everybody loves killing tankers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:51.98,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Update 1.77 Advancing Storm added new top-level ground vehicles to the game
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:55.26,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,such as the Abrams, the T-64B, and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:07:00.90,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs49}And needless to say, this has affected the balance and changed the game at high ranks and battle ratings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:11.06,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs48}In general, right now (filmed 5 days after release) we're satisfied with how they've been received by players
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:13.00,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,and how they've impacted the game's balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:19.98,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs42}But introducing top-level vehicles is bound to change the balance of all previous vehicles and will always change the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.66,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's a whole new adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:33.56,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs39}We're therefore going to have to take another look at all of the battle ratings affected by this change, so our work here has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.82,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Write to us and tell us what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:42.18,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs53}Leave feedback in the forum or the comments, because your feedback is as important as statistics
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:45.40,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,They're the two primary part of the information we work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:55.72,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs42}However, while statistics show us dry facts, it doesn't do a great job of telling us how changes have been received by players
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.70,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,or how they're affected the way the game feels to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:02.46,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,In order to get this information we need to watch our players play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.38,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We need you to leave us feedback so we can read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:08.82,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,So write to us, we always study your feedback carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:14.96,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs48}There will definitely be changes, both to things that are already in the game and things that are yet to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:21.50,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs53}It always happens. But right now... right now players have been pretty positive about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:32.90,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,I hope you liked update 1.77 Advancing Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:36.20,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We spent over six months working on it, almost a year
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.16,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,and we put a lot of effort into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:43.50,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Send us your feedback, write comments, "like" us, and subscribe to our channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:10.90,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,大家好 我叫Kirill Yudintsev 我是Gaijin的创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:16.38,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,现在我想告诉你一些关于1.77前行暴风这个最新更新的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,0:00:23.70,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们收到了很多最新的更新的反馈 感谢您写信给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:26.32,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,你们的反馈对我们非常重要和有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:33.94,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,除此之外 很多反馈都是关于新引擎 新渲染器 新图形以及游戏性能的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:37.80,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,一些玩家的游戏性能表现有所改善 而其他玩家的则变得更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:43.46,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,有些声称自己游戏性能变差的玩家 正在使用超级采样（SSAA x4）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:47.66,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,超采样是最耗费资源的反锯齿形式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:54.40,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们不建议启用它 除非你的显卡功能非常强大 譬如说在没开抗锯齿的时候能达到200FPS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:01:01.06,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,对于其他人来说 在性能方面有更简单的选项 并且可以提供同样优秀的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:06.04,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,使用HQ TAA 只是TAA 甚至是HQ FXAA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:11.26,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这些都是非常不错的抗锯齿类型 可以提供非常好的图像质量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:23.26,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,新引擎赋予游戏很多新功能 但我们仍然有一些工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:25.84,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,并且有改善优化的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:31.64,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这些新功能需要大量配置 我们需要考虑很多细微差别
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:35.62,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这个更新刚刚出来 并在接下来的六个月的某个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:40.24,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们将改进游戏外观的各个方面以及其性能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:46.18,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,所以如果你的游戏性能变得更糟 也许我们以后能找到某种方法来改善
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:53.68,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,许多玩家一直在问关于海战的情况 以及战雷海战的内测的内测(先行封闭beta测试)进展情况
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:57.06,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,它的最终命运将是什么 以及我们未来的计划是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:02.86,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,测试进展顺利 我们做了很多事情 总的来说 我们的待办事项清单并不是很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.82,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们很快就要进行内测(封闭beta测试)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:09.00,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,过去两年来 海战发生了深刻的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:14.88,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,从内测开始到现在变化很大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:20.12,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这些改变特别要感谢我们的玩家 以及他们的反馈和意见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:24.28,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们一直在听他们的意见 看他们玩 自己测试或者和玩家一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:36.38,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们的目标是让每件事都变得有趣和吸引人 而且我们不希望海战让我们的玩家失望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.88,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们希望它能够满足玩家的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:42.70,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,就我们而言 我们已经完成了几乎所有我们可以做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:45.44,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们想要的一切 以及我们玩家想要的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:48.62,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,换句话说 我们正处于这个初始阶段的末尾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.86,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们的玩家经常会问我们未来的飞机计划是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:03:01.04,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,他们想知道为什么我们老是为坦克玩家提供各种各样的东西 包括现代坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:03.52,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,然而飞机这边都是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:09.04,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我应该首先指出的是 在我们引入地面载具之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:13.26,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们专注于开发空战四年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:20.58,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,自从我们引入地面载具后又过了四年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:24.60,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,在那段时间里 我们从未停止过同时开发游戏的两部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:30.78,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,只是我们可以为飞机实现的大多数最重要的事情已经实施了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:34.54,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,譬如 我们每年都会增加一些相当重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.96,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们最近发布的炮手视角
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:44.44,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,而且在同一次更新中让飞机可以因空投与炸弹的碰撞而被摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:55.24,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,{\fs65}总的来说 我们一直在更新各种各样的东西 因为所有的大功能已经完成 现在更新的都是小功能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:04:00.20,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,下一个空战中的主要更新很可能引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:07.28,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我指的是更现代的超音速飞机 导弹和其他现代航空技术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:17.40,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,正如我刚才所说 我们一直在持续进行内部测试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.42,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,并不是没有目标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:27.02,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,由于导弹 探测系统和超音速 这个程度的载具让游戏机制变得更复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:42.12,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,所有空战玩家都知道 喷气式飞机已经与活塞式飞机的玩法有显着不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:45.14,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,有很多人不喜欢这种差异
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:49.86,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,未来的变化更会改变游戏 所以我们正在努力和测试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:55.12,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,而现在我还没准备好说更多的现代飞机肯定会出现在游戏中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:59.92,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,但仍有很多机会推出某种类型的更为现代化的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:05.32,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我无法给你任何细节 我们仍处于研究和实验阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.52,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,目标是确定“上限”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:12.46,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,还有一个问题是 不同生产模式的载具变得越来越少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:15.44,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,所以平衡各个国家成为问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:21.62,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,游戏中有很多细微差别和问题 这是一个非常复杂的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.64,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,平衡 以及如何向玩家解释这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:35.94,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,如你所知 我们不发明载具或者不改变已有载具的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:41.70,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,正如生活需要平衡 游戏载具也需要平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:47.58,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,一般来说 有很多工作 我们的大多数玩家不一定会对结果感到满意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.88,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这就是说 在我们的游戏中 你不需要玩每个载具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:55.06,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,遇到了不喜欢的载具就不要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:06:02.88,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,所以我们仍然在为喜欢它的玩家做这件事 但我现在仍无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:09.30,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,另外 我们也在试验直升机 既有攻击直升机也有其他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:13.28,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这件事推进得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:18.98,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,对于玩家来说 这种游戏玩法通常会更简单和容易理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:24.38,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,尽管直升机比飞机更难飞 但它们也更慢 火力也更小
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:34.58,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,射击距离更短 飞行员在驾驶和射击方面的影响力更大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:39.86,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,所以在现代飞机出现之前 直升机完全有可能出现在我们的游戏中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:45.56,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,他们也更适合用于陆战模式 每个人都喜欢舔地 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:51.98,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,更新1.77前行暴风增加了新的顶级地面车辆的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:55.26,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,如艾布拉姆斯 T-64B等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:07:00.90,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,不用说 这已经影响了平衡 并改变了游戏的高级别和战斗等级
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:11.06,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,一般来说 现在（时间点是发布后的5天内）我们对他们被玩家的接受程度感到满意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:13.00,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,以及他们如何影响游戏的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:19.98,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,但是引进顶级车辆势必会改变以前所有车辆的平衡 并且会一直改变游戏规则
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.66,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,换句话说 这是一个全新的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:33.56,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,因此 我们将不得不重新审视受这一变化影响的所有战斗权重 所以我们的工作才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.82,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,写邮件给我们 告诉我们你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:42.18,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,在论坛或评论中留下反馈 因为你的反馈与统计数据一样重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:45.40,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,它们是我们所使用信息的两个主要部分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:55.72,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,然而 虽然统计数据显示我们有些枯燥的事实 但它并没有很好地告诉我们玩家如何接受改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.70,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,或者他们如何影响游戏对他们的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:02.46,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,为了获得这些信息 我们需要观看我们的玩家进行比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.38,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们需要您留下反馈意见 以便我们阅读
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:08.82,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,所以写信给我们 我们总是仔细研究您的反馈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:14.96,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,游戏中已有的东西和未来的东西肯定会发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:21.50,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,它总是发生 但现在 现在玩家们对所有事情都非常积极
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:32.90,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我希望你喜欢更新1.77前行暴风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:36.20,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们花了六个月的时间研究它 差不多一年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.16,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们付出了很多努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:43.50,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,向我们发送您的反馈 写下评论 “喜欢”我们 并订阅我们的频道！
